WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:09.831
Hey, good morning, family. Praise the Lord. Day 48—we're almost to 50, Braden.

00:00:09.832 --> 00:00:18.552
It's a celebration: 50 videos, not in a row but close. We just want to say thank you all for joining us today.

00:00:18.553 --> 00:00:24.493
For all the new people, if this is your first video and you've never been here before, welcome.

00:00:24.494 --> 00:00:29.523
Welcome to all the faithful people who have been here for so long; we really appreciate it.

00:00:29.524 --> 00:00:38.715
If you could like the video, subscribe if you haven't, and click the notification bell. It would really bless us and help us with the algorithm.

00:00:38.716 --> 00:00:48.093
It truly does help us every time I say something silly and you start commenting on it; it boosts that thing way up in the algorithm.

00:00:48.094 --> 00:01:03.938
We laugh about it because Braden says, 'Hey, I'm glad you messed up today, Dad, because it helped our video,'since he watches all the analytics.

00:01:03.939 --> 00:01:15.933
I don't understand all that, but he's really smart. I've had a lot of emails—Diana says we've had a lot of emails—wanting to know about the Five Pillars.

00:01:15.934 --> 00:01:29.432
Ladies and gentlemen, I've had people who are not very educated about crypto jump into something they don't know and then say, 'Well, you told me to do it.'I've never told anybody to do anything; I'll stick by that.

00:01:29.433 --> 00:01:43.382
I am not a financial advisor. I tell you what I feel the Lord has told me about crypto, gold, silver, and land.

00:01:43.383 --> 00:01:48.925
He talks to me about all kinds of things, but rarely about stocks.

00:01:48.926 --> 00:01:57.102
Every so often He will, but I'm not here to advise you on your finances.

00:01:57.103 --> 00:02:05.600
I know some people understand that, but there are some who just don't.

00:02:05.601 --> 00:02:19.637
This is for entertainment purposes only. I am not telling you to buy, sell, or do anything. This is my opinion, and I'm entitled to it.

00:02:19.638 --> 00:02:35.359
I believe in what the Lord has told me, and I say you should go out and pray, asking the Holy Spirit what He wants you to do with your finances.

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:46.719
Do not invest in something unless you're educated, and do not do anything with your money until the Holy Spirit tells you to.

00:02:46.720 --> 00:03:01.802
It's very important you know this; what I pray about might not be for you. Everybody's walk is different.

00:03:01.803 --> 00:03:14.342
Whenever I'm talking about the Five Pillars, I saw five major cryptocurrencies that will be the pillars of all crypto.

00:03:14.343 --> 00:03:20.695
There will be five: three are very strong, and there's one that's the strongest.

00:03:20.696 --> 00:03:30.551
I saw one in the middle, two on the side of it, and then two more over.

00:03:30.552 --> 00:03:47.098
They were standing like Greek or Roman columns made of solid granite.

00:03:47.099 --> 00:03:58.626
The Holy Spirit showed me support systems on these columns, which were other cryptocurrencies that line up with the functions of those main ones.

00:03:58.627 --> 00:04:24.112
There were probably five or so helping each main coin, propping it up.

00:04:24.113 --> 00:04:53.274
Then I saw falling stars—all the other cryptos that had no real function, which I would call scams, started falling like internet code and ceased to exist. Thousands of them disappeared in the vision.

00:04:53.275 --> 00:05:23.278
Then I heard 'governmental regulations.'I saw bills being passed to make it stable because I heard 'Wild West,'and laws were being brought into motion to protect investors so they would not be scammed.

00:05:23.279 --> 00:05:38.323
They were going to regulate it, and then I saw 'old money'—the elderly people with big money—starting to put their money in because they felt safe.

00:05:38.324 --> 00:05:57.281
Right now, it's the Wild West with no laws. Look at all the stuff that has happened even before Donald Trump has been sworn into office.

00:05:57.282 --> 00:06:07.997
It is like a rocket ship. You can see the 5, 4, 3, 2, 1, and the smoke before liftoff.

00:06:07.998 --> 00:06:22.351
He's not even in office yet, but everyone is anticipating who he's going to put as the head of the SEC who is pro-crypto.

00:06:22.351 --> 00:06:28.323
I don't follow all this stuff; I just pray, and the Lord gives me visions.

00:06:28.324 --> 00:06:39.439
However, that doesn't mean it's for today or even five years from now; I don't know the time frame.

00:06:39.440 --> 00:06:52.802
Braden and I were looking at when Kim Clement gave his word about XMP and all the things the Lord showed him; that was 12 or 13 years ago.

00:06:52.803 --> 00:07:08.399
If people tried to figure out what XMP was back then, they would have been disappointed when the lawsuit came in and it went down to 15 cents.

00:07:08.400 --> 00:07:20.661
XMP was what it was. You have prophetic words given by people who see in the spirit, but you never know the timing.

00:07:20.662 --> 00:07:34.605
There is depth perception to the prophetic. You don't know when that 'oak tree'is coming to pass.

00:07:34.606 --> 00:07:50.396
As of right now, that word has still not fully manifested or hit the all-time high he was talking about.

00:07:50.397 --> 00:08:03.432
You have to use discernment and wisdom, not just get on a 'Holy Ghost bandwagon'listening to men on the internet.

00:08:03.433 --> 00:08:11.809
You have to hear it inside yourself because it is volatile. It goes up and down, and it freaks me out.

00:08:11.810 --> 00:08:41.880
Who knows if it will fall by a dollar or ten? You must know the Holy Spirit is leading you.

00:08:41.881 --> 00:08:50.332
My son was showing me that everybody, their brother, and their dog is prophesying about XMP and other things.

00:08:50.333 --> 00:09:05.573
There is a ton of prophetic work out there, and I'm not dogging them—who am I to say anything about those people?—but you have to be very discerning.

00:09:05.574 --> 00:09:18.575
You might be hearing something out of the flesh just because 'Billy Bob'said it and you want to make a viral video too.

00:09:18.576 --> 00:09:58.934
There are 'bandwagon prophets'out there. I saw five main things, and I saw regulation coming in. I saw stability and increase.

00:09:58.935 --> 00:11:04.731
The Lord said to me, 'The very thing the body of Christ is trying to embrace right now is the very thing that leads to the mark of the beast.'A cashless society is part of the end-time system; it's the technology behind what's coming with the chip, and none of you are going to want that.

00:11:04.732 --> 00:11:13.320
There's just so much to it in the spirit realm. Would I like to tell you about the other four pillars?

00:11:13.321 --> 00:11:30.129
Yes, my heart would love to, but I can't. If I go into all that, you'll put all your money into them.

00:11:30.130 --> 00:11:40.261
I've already gotten emails from people saying they put their life inheritance in.

00:11:40.262 --> 00:11:51.738
Why would you do that? Only do what you can afford if the Lord tells you to.

00:11:51.739 --> 00:12:08.874
I work too hard for my money; I know how much it takes to sell stuff on eBay to pay an electric bill.

00:12:08.875 --> 00:12:43.756
If you put money into crypto, you have to look at it like going to the movies or buying fireworks—that money is gone once it's spent.

00:12:43.757 --> 00:12:52.752
I know what the Lord has shown me, but we are just imperfect vessels.

00:12:52.753 --> 00:13:15.838
Pure water can come from the Father, but if it comes through a tainted pipe, the water becomes tainted.

00:13:15.839 --> 00:13:28.224
You have to watch what you're hearing on the internet. I have compassion for folks, but there are desperate people doing dumb things.

00:13:28.225 --> 00:13:37.998
I've had family members say they are going to put advances on their credit cards.

00:13:37.999 --> 00:13:56.999
Hold on a minute; that's not God. God is not a god of debt. He said to owe no man anything but to love him. I do not believe in borrowing money on credit cards.

00:13:57.000 --> 00:14:25.159
If you have a car note or a house payment to have a nice home, that's one thing, but borrowing with high interest rates is a trap that keeps you from being free.

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:43.516
If God doesn't provide it, I don't need it. He's going to give us creative ideas to get wealth and revelation knowledge.

00:14:43.517 --> 00:15:05.026
I believe if you sow a seed, you'll reap a harvest. I believe more in that than anything.

00:15:05.027 --> 00:15:38.336
God provides for His kids, and it's not a chance thing; it's seedtime and harvest. Reaping is a law just as much as sowing is.

00:15:38.337 --> 00:15:54.006
I believe in the hundredfold return and that the Lord will bless our hands to prosper. I believe in that more than any kind of crypto.

00:15:54.007 --> 00:16:25.691
There was so much talk about the dinar for years, or network marketing pyramid schemes promising you'll be rich.

00:16:25.692 --> 00:16:41.660
There's nothing inherently wrong with network marketing, but often you get to the top and they promise so much.

00:16:41.661 --> 00:17:04.664
I remember people at church always trying to do network marketing; you'd try to avoid them in the hall because you knew they'd try to sell you Amway.

00:17:04.665 --> 00:17:24.198
Many people have contacted me to do network marketing on this platform, asking me to sign up under them and promote it to you all.

00:17:24.199 --> 00:17:31.199
I've told you: I am not going to sell anything to anybody on this channel. I will never ask you for money.

00:17:31.200 --> 00:17:44.519
I put my merch on there because people asked for it, but I don't even promote it.

00:17:44.520 --> 00:18:03.597
This channel will always be about Jesus Christ and His coming. It's never going to be a crypto channel.

00:18:03.598 --> 00:18:27.476
My heart is to tell you that He's coming soon and you need to get your house in order. I had more to talk about today, but that took too much time.

00:18:27.477 --> 00:18:44.830
Tomorrow I'll tell you about the man who flew from Australia to Oklahoma to warn me about a vision I had of an EMP attack on America.

00:18:44.831 --> 00:19:01.246
He felt the Holy Spirit told him to warn me about a Chinese company that bought a grain refinery on the Mississippi River.

00:19:01.247 --> 00:19:30.359
I told you all about a barge floating up the Mississippi River that was owned by a Chinese company.

00:19:30.360 --> 00:19:36.309
The government tried to stop the sale, but the state sold it anyway.

00:19:36.310 --> 00:19:57.954
This barge I saw coming down the Mississippi went out into the Gulf and had a rocket on it that said 'USSR.'When they shot it over America, it didn't get high enough, and the EMP only affected areas like Kentucky.

00:19:57.955 --> 00:20:18.239
This was a vision of a surprise attack from Asian people—I don't know if they were Chinese or North Korean.

00:20:18.240 --> 00:20:39.172
The Lord told me they were coming for grains. Seeing this company buy a grain refinery on the Mississippi sent alarm bells off inside me.

00:20:39.173 --> 00:21:13.124
It's not a coincidence; it's like a Trojan surprise attack from the Gulf of Mexico. It's something to pray about.

00:21:13.125 --> 00:22:28.918
If you study enough, the Five Pillars are pretty obvious, but the safe way is to let the Holy Spirit show you. Father, I thank You for every person here.

00:22:28.919 --> 00:22:37.283
I thank You that no weapon formed against them shall prosper and that they would have wisdom in what to invest in.

00:22:37.284 --> 00:22:52.880
Let them follow the voice of the Holy Spirit, not a trend or a fad. I ask that they have ears to hear.

00:22:52.881 --> 00:24:30.542
We take authority over hype and all demonic attacks from scammers.

00:24:30.543 --> 00:24:47.348
We thank You, Lord, that the body of Christ will be protected.

00:24:47.349 --> 00:27:12.791
You are our Shepherd; You lead us beside still waters and restore our souls.

00:27:12.792 --> 00:27:18.682
We take authority over the demonic spirits trying to come against President Trump.

00:27:18.683 --> 00:27:29.038
We thank You that he is protected—that a thousand shall fall at his side and ten thousand at his right hand, but nothing shall come near him.

00:27:29.039 --> 00:27:43.046
We thank You that his family is protected and that any plans of the wicked will be uncovered.

00:27:43.047 --> 00:28:27.058
We cover the vice presidency and RFK Jr. in the blood of Jesus as he works to bring out the evil in the Food and Drug Administration.

00:28:27.059 --> 00:29:11.831
We thank You that there will be justice for the seeds of evil sown in the past.

00:29:11.832 --> 00:30:26.967
We claim back sevenfold everything the devil stole. We call for restitution—not just in finances, but in time and health.

00:30:26.968 --> 00:30:48.909
Just as You delivered the children of Israel out of Egypt, You will deliver Your people now.

00:30:48.910 --> 00:31:32.916
We call for financial increase and sweatless victories. We are debt-free, the head and not the tail.

00:31:32.917 --> 00:32:59.591
We plead the blood of Jesus over every negative seed we've sown in ignorance and call for crop failure on those bad seeds.

00:32:59.592 --> 00:33:06.448
Every seed produces after its own kind; how you treat people is a seed.

00:33:06.449 --> 00:34:26.874
Seedtime and harvest will never cease. We thank You, Father, for the hostages to be released in Israel. We pray for the peace of Jerusalem.

00:34:26.875 --> 00:35:16.274
We thank You that all darkness is exposed in that camp and that the innocent Palestinian children and women are protected.

00:35:16.275 --> 00:35:59.727
We thank You for the oil and gas wealth about to spring forth in Israel and for a fresh breath on the Abrahamic Covenant.

00:35:59.728 --> 00:37:21.877
We ask for protection for Trump until he is sworn in. We thank You that all evil plans of the current administration will be uncovered.

00:37:21.878 --> 00:37:26.319
I told you that eventually, America, Canada, and Mexico would have a digital currency joined as three nations.

00:37:26.320 --> 00:38:06.037
Trump already told Trudeau he has a plan for that. He knows what's going on with the BRICS nations and the dollar.

00:38:06.038 --> 00:39:10.003
Father, give him Solomon-like wisdom to lead this nation. We thank You that corruption will be uncovered in the House and Senate and that godly leaders will rise up.

00:39:10.004 --> 00:40:34.035
We pray for Elon Musk to be born again and filled with the Holy Spirit. We call forth the laborers to bring in the lost.

00:40:34.036 --> 00:41:15.135
We call for revival over Asia, South Korea, China, and the underground church.

00:41:15.136 --> 00:41:18.916
We pray for revival in Venezuela, Cuba, Jamaica, and all the islands.

00:41:18.917 --> 00:42:40.561
We call for revival in Africa, England, Europe, Australia, and Queensland.

00:42:40.562 --> 00:43:28.842
Stir the hearts of the preachers to be bold. We praise You for a new hunger and thirst after righteousness.

00:43:28.843 --> 00:43:43.358
We call marriages restored and bodies healed. Thank you for joining me today.

00:43:43.359 --> 00:44:00.630
I appreciate all the support and kindness during this Christmas season.

00:44:00.631 --> 00:44:31.525
Happy Birthday, Jesus! He is my Lord and Savior. We always have a cake for Him as a family and sing Happy Birthday.

00:44:31.526 --> 00:45:16.535
Some might think that's silly, but He loves it. If you make a place for Him in your house, He'll visit you.

00:45:16.536 --> 00:46:28.052
Come to Him as a child, not an adult. He is the Lord of the Harvest, and all He cares about is your heart.

00:46:28.053 --> 00:46:36.129
He died for you and rose again so you wouldn't have to go through hell.

00:46:36.130 --> 00:47:11.950
I've seen the holes in His hands and feet; He did it all for you.

00:47:11.951 --> 00:47:25.409
All you have to do is receive it by faith. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:47:25.410 --> 00:47:37.280
Jesus loves you so much, and we will see you again tomorrow. Bye-bye.

